X_2=0@0:void := querylog.define("select c_name, c_custkey, o_orderkey,
 o_orderdate, o_totalprice, sum(l_quantity)
from customer, orders, lineitem
where o_orderkey in (
 select l_orderkey
 from lineitem
 group by l_orderkey having
 sum(l_quantity) > 300
 )
 and c_custkey = o_custkey
 and o_orderkey = l_orderkey
group by c_name, c_custkey,
 o_orderkey, o_orderdate, o_totalprice
order by o_totalprice desc, o_orderdate
limit 100;":str, "sequential_pipe":str, 172:int);
